{"tid":2328942,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"教協強調不支持港獨 斥央視節目失實","createTime":"2020-12-17T01:39:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T07:41:18.000Z","uid":156254,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7d4eaeb1f86499e66caccaa8aa6faebd8148e9a4","tid":2328942,"uid":156254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T01:39:38.000Z","msg":"教協強調不支持港獨 斥央視節目失實 <br />\n本地 發佈時間 17.12.2020 09:23 最後更新時間 17.12.2020 09:23 <br />\n<br />\n教協副會長葉建源在本台節目表示，中央電視台早前製作有關香港的節目，安排在3間本港電視台播放，認爲當中不少内容嚴重失實，包括指教協支持中學生宣揚港獨、煽動學生到維園示威，他指教協不支持港獨、亦不會向學生灌輸任何政治理念，而有關示威是一場教師遊行，與學生無關。 葉建源指，教協6月寫信予通訊事務管理局，投訴3個本港電視台在有關事件上處理不當，令教協蒙受抹黑，並在昨日收到回覆。葉建源引述局方指投訴不成立，因本港對外購節目有特別處理，他質疑是雙重標準，認爲即使是外購節目，電視台同樣有責任把關内容。他要求局方重新審視及解釋有關決定。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2371004\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2371004&d=c%2B6PkbrQ5MzYtHY5m9tE1xdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=c73c6e18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2371004</a><br />\n<br />\n老共 老屈教協, 要食死貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1fc04bd47dd74f42cf701ae33716ab3cc8ad04d","tid":2328942,"uid":41873,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T01:40:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bw3EVgj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbw3EVgj.png&h=8b9c7ad6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ead002e17538341675469baed48c391c9b4dadb","tid":2328942,"uid":237562,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T02:42:49.000Z","msg":"你跪得姿勢唔啱就係港獨啦柒頭"},